## Limitations

The research was limited by the availability of full-text documents and the reliance on secondary sources, which may not capture the full complexity of the historical context. Additionally, the focus was primarily on American reform movements, which may not fully represent the global scope of women's activism during this period. Further research could benefit from primary sources and a broader geographical perspective.